      "date": "2013-01-18 07:44:03.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/2eee877a-613c-11e2-be04-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  3 tests failed: recovery-small, replay-single, sanity.",
