        "subject": "LU-2513 osc: fix grants calculation.",
        "message": "LU-2513 osc: fix grants calculation.\n\ntotal grants in system should be don't exceed the dirty size limit.\nalso we don't want to send two or more grants requests to the ost.\nalso grants should be don't compared with max brw size as it's\nlimited by dirty size, not a max rpc's.\n\nXyratex-bug-id: MRP-809\nSigned-off-by: Alexey Lyashkov <alexey_lyashkov@xyratex.com>\nChange-Id: I8502defbf5032a94fd8e269bc58f9e2c2bdf7757\n"
